"A boolean indicating whether to use A1 style notation (TRUE) or R1C1 style "
"notation (FALSE)."
msgstr ""
"Boolean koji označava treba li koristiti A1 stil notacije (TRUE) ili R1C1 "
"stil notacije (FALSE)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"A boolean; if TRUE, empty cells selected in the text arguments won't be "
"included in the result."
msgstr ""
"Boolean; ako je TRUE, prazne ćelije odabrane u tekstualnim argumentima neće "
"biti uključene u rezultat."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
